name: Fruitful
description:
Sometimes we feel as if we have never had enough when we compare ourselves to others. Sometimes we just need to orient ourselves. Be happy with what we have. Feeling content in life with the gifts given and enjoying every moment in life. Knowing that our values are complete, embracing our uniqueness and really being able to live our own lives well is the true meaning of a fruitful life.
